{"tid":2463133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[韓國起源]被指歪曲史實、使用中式道具　南韓古裝劇停播","createTime":"2021-03-26T12:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T13:04:46.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3a1744ea5935b271b91b16c83f4d8ac01a739d","tid":2463133,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T12:54:31.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】南韓有古裝電視劇被指歪曲史實及使用中式道具，要停播。<br />\n耗資320億韓元、即近2.2億港元拍攝的這套古裝韓劇，播出首兩集引起廣泛批評。劇集以朝鮮時代作背景，但出現月餅、皮蛋等中式食物，部分角色亦穿著中式服裝。劇中，朝鮮太宗濫殺百姓的情節被指醜化其形象、歪曲歷史。<br />\n兩日已有逾20萬人在青瓦台網頁聯署，要求停播劇集。加上劇集贊助商全部撤資，電視台和製作公司決定停播這套韓劇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/728180?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_campaign=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR0yuVbg7V_m3ZXqRPHxtbU43oIFlEBPNbH0bgnhV6w-uy2FD8jot_3sZjM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F728180%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_campaign%3Dshare%26fbclid%3DIwAR0yuVbg7V_m3ZXqRPHxtbU43oIFlEBPNbH0bgnhV6w-uy2FD8jot_3sZjM&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWpE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=44ff2867\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F728180%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_campaign%3Dshare%26fbclid%3DIwAR0yuVbg7V_m3ZXqRPHxtbU43oIFlEBPNbH0bgnhV6w-uy2FD8jot_3sZjM&h=6e25d2ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/728180?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_campaign=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR0yuVbg7V_m3ZXqRPHxtbU43oIFlEBPNbH0bgnhV6w-uy2FD8jot_3sZjM</a>"},{"pid":"70c92ac28d9e09b4c40a669b93684e999d9ea2b4","tid":2463133,"uid":54125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:04:46.000Z","msg":"係咪搵咗支那人做staff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}